data.description: Don't miss your opportunity to own in the 55+ community of Laurel Gardens. This 3 bedroom (plus bonus workshop room) and 2 bathroom home features an open layout. The master bedroom is spacious with a walk-in closet and bathroom featuring a walk-in shower. The guest bathroom has a bathtub and built-in vanity space. The kitchen has plenty of cabinets and opens to a large dining room area and Arizona room. This leads out to the oversized covered patio and tranquil backyard. Through the backyard is the 2 car carport, storage shed and additional slab parking space. The community features a pool that is just a few doors down.
